eu.trentorise.smartcampus.osm.android.tileprovider

Class MapTile

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.trentorise.smartcampus.osm.android.tileprovider.MapTile

  • public class MapTile
extends java.lang.Object
    A map tile is distributed using the observer pattern. The tile is delivered by a tile provider (i.e. a descendant of MapTileModuleProviderBase or MapTileProviderBase to a consumer of tiles (e.g. descendant of TilesOverlay). Tiles are typically images (e.g. png or jpeg).
